README - info file

* About the Sqlite3 DBD driver

 This a driver for guile-dbi to use a sqlite3 database.

 Connection string format:
  <database name>


Maintainer hints:

	To build a clean, fresh tool envirnoment:

		libtoolize
		aclocal
		autoscan
		autoheader
		automake
		autoconf
		./configure
